    {
      "html": "Very neat, regular small letters of fairly square module. Omicon and omega of more or less equal size to other letters. Alpha with straight bar; epsilon with short middle bar; Omega circular and open. Pronounced terminal serifs visible on some letters, e.g. epsilon and tau."
